---
// Ecosystem Component (Golden Path Architecture)
// Features animated "vine" lines and a responsive grid of growth stages.
---

<section id="ecosystem" class="py-24 bg-foundry-surface/50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-foundry-primary mb-4">Golden Path Architecture</h2>
      <p class="text-foundry-text/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg italic">"Visualizing the organic growth of your project's infrastructure."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Responsive Vine Lines (Animated) -->
      <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 1000 400">
        <path 
          class="vine-line" 
          d="M125,100 Q250,100 250,200 T375,300 Q500,300 500,100 T625,100 Q750,100 750,200 T875,300" 
          stroke="var(--color-foundry-secondary)" 
          stroke-width="2" 
          fill="none" 
        />
      </svg>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative z-10">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-foundry-accent/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-foundry-secondary transition-all group glass-panel animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-foundry-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl">ðŸŒ±</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-foundry-primary mb-3">Seed Stage</h3>
          <p class="text-foundry-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Initial germination of ideas. Rapid prototyping environment with pre-built component soil.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-foundry-secondary bg-foundry-secondary/10 w-fit px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">
            <code>git init</code>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-foundry-accent/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-foundry-secondary transition-all group glass-panel mt-0 md:mt-24 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-foundry-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl">ðŸŒ¿</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-foundry-primary mb-3">Root System</h3>
          <p class="text-foundry-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Establishing core architecture. Hexagonal patterns ensuring your logic remains pure and adaptable.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-foundry-secondary bg-foundry-secondary/10 w-fit px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">
            <code>make setup</code>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-foundry-accent/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-foundry-secondary transition-all group glass-panel animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-foundry-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl">ðŸ”‹</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-foundry-primary mb-3">Stem Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-foundry-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Vertical scaling. Automated deployment pipelines that branch your product across multiple regions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-foundry-secondary bg-foundry-secondary/10 w-fit px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">
            <code>sscli deploy</code>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-foundry-accent/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-foundry-secondary transition-all group glass-panel mt-0 md:mt-24 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-foundry-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-3xl">ðŸ¦‹</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-2xl text-foundry-primary mb-3">Bloom Era</h3>
          <p class="text-foundry-text/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The polished user experience. A thriving, multidisciplinary interface that captures value and grows.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-foundry-secondary bg-foundry-secondary/10 w-fit px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">
            <code>v1.0.0</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
